name: Untitled_IDKA_04
description: "Untitled I Don't Know Anymore" is a series of short looping videos cobbled together from the remnants of a completely different project that shriveled up during the pandemic. The animation originates from the artist's motion capture session and recorded footage of their live liquid light show. These raw materials were used to generate simulations. They were also processed and reprocessed and and layered and processed even more. The final stage was reduction from a full 9 minute (13,000+ frames)
